name: compute_cosine_similarity
parameters_schema: {\"embedding1\": {\"type\": \"array\", \"description\": \"First vector embedding (list of floats)\", \"required\": true}, \"embedding2\": {\"type\": \"array\", \"description\": \"Second vector embedding (list of floats)\", \"required\": true}}

name: find_similar_prompts_by_embedding

description: Find similar prompts in Neo4j database using vector embedding similarity

name: reconstruct_cached_plan

name: synthesis_helper_tool
parameters_schema: {\"synthesis_text\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"The synthesized answer text to persist or post-process\", \"required\": true}, \"format\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"Optional format (text|json)\", \"required\": false}}
description: Helper tool invoked by the synthesis agent to format and persist the final synthesized answer.

name: text_summarizer
parameters_schema: {\"text\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"The text to summarize\", \"required\": true}, \"max_length\": {\"type\": \"integer\", \"description\": \"Maximum length of summary in words\", \"required\": false}}
description: Summarize long text into key points
